{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0516047fc7","title":"关于幹部政策的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"75f27e162b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0516047fc7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"070633ff8f","name":"董光亚"},{"id":"1983af3f82","name":"姚明"},{"id":"2891d8f050","name":"王革"},{"id":"3d4be61a08","name":"钱骅"},{"id":"4c586bcd7b","name":"田本陆"},{"id":"56779d4fc7","name":"章文岳"},{"id":"7bf9452ead","name":"王文庆"},{"id":"8e4fd0657c","name":"汪天一"},{"id":"aba2881e68","name":"陈述庆"},{"id":"b9d6e9c96b","name":"北京政法学院"},{"id":"f16a0f1a33","name":"林共鸣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3234d07fa6","type":"title","text":"关于干部政策的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"4831fe557a","type":"authors","text":"北京政法学院汪天一姚明章文岳王革陈述庆林共鸣董光亚钱骅王文庆田本陆","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"b76d204892","type":"paragraph","text":"“不管党外人士怎样，都不可能和党完全一样，不能一条心，不然便不符合马列主义的辩证法。”(汪天一)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"b8df45994d","type":"paragraph","text":"姚明说：“党组织，包庇党员，对群众却很严，好像家丑不可外扬，党员偷东西就不处理。”又说：“党支部对我、姚海峰、张珂、赵瑛完全不信任。”“提意见越尖锐越好，不要四平八稳，在整风中群众最积极，团员次之，党员最落后”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"1b2054c254","type":"paragraph","text":"“确实他们(指二年一班党员)并不把党委会、党纪放在眼里。事实证明，党委会不会去处分他们，要处分的是非党人士。”(章文岳)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"ca5b901cd9","type":"paragraph","text":"王革说：“党的干部政策就是：党员第一，团员第二，群众第三。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"2d91484a8c","type":"paragraph","text":"陈述庆说：“党组织把群众分为三等——先进，中间，落后。如果这种分法被群众知道了，这是对人格的污辱。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"3fae6f0be8","type":"paragraph","text":"林共鸣说：“党员是戴金牌的，团员是戴银牌的，群众是戴铁牌的，不小心就会生锈。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"6b4a8e1ac3","type":"paragraph","text":"章文岳说：党员干部“不懂装懂，排斥异端”，“这里的职务大都为党员干部包办了。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"a306b090ec","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在班里是这样的，(指干部政策)：首先考虑党员，然后考虑团员，没有群众的分……再看这些党员(党员干部)怎么样，不称职。”(姚明)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"2ad92ee50a","type":"paragraph","text":"林共鸣煽动说：“我们班上，现在没有可能当班长，李绪孝倒是不坏，可以当班长，他很果断，勇敢。群众不是没有能力当班长，通过这次整风，你可以当付班长了(对蔡文辉说)。”又说：“你们怕什么，怕死鬼，群众已动起来了，你们还怕什么！”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"a4dfafdb00","type":"paragraph","text":"“干部都是党员，这是宗派主义。过去工作都是党员包办的。如作报告，欢迎外宾。”(董光亚)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"52613b030c","type":"paragraph","text":"“我院人事工作不是为了工作需要，只是为了给老干部以‘长’的名义。”(钱骅)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"6f6f23ecc1","type":"paragraph","text":"王文庆写道：“学校为工农开门，工农去年优先录取，本是好事，然而工农学生考试不及格，刘教务长却要讲师给添成5分，4分，又主要按政治质量、品质及觉悟程度给分，而不论其考试成绩，真是善哉善！阿弥陀佛！”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"3d4892b6e1","type":"paragraph","text":"林共鸣说：“党组织对华侨照顾不够，另眼看待，甚至把华侨当作客人，不愿和华侨接近。”“党支部认为华侨落后到无可救药，党支部破坏了华侨政策。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"fb6c00f022","type":"subtitle","text":"田本陆的诗：","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"4cfdf43aab","type":"paragraph","text":"春风一吹杏花开，非党群众哭的哀，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"4b31bda643","type":"paragraph","text":"都是同根生的啊，为啥白眼把咱待。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"23a143536e","type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"17a7a70d7f","type":"paragraph","text":"党员拿钱不费难，咱们穷死没人管。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"32981a4818","type":"paragraph","text":"补丁罗补丁啊，谁来邻惜咱，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"233c31011b","type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"6d1f32d829","type":"paragraph","text":"党员打人不算数，咱们的通报飞满天","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"d9bdc15fb0","type":"paragraph","text":"秋风扫落叶啊，谁来教育咱","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"0cb72a0bfc","type":"paragraph","text":"一朝天子一朝臣，官场的座位党员占","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"dffd3fb32b","type":"paragraph","text":"无职又无权啊，何时把身翻。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"},{"id":"3efddbe0fe","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《北京政法学院右派分子言行汇编》(第1部分)(北京政法学院，1957年10月)。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7"}],"page":{"id":"70fedca942","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0516047fc7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}